      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "I&#39;d say 99% of visitors here are encountering what I encounter about once per year with Eclipse. There&#39;s apparently a bug in eclipse that causes this &quot;Skip All Breakpoints&quot; feature to turn ON all by itself even though you didn&#39;t actually turn it on."
